    <p>👾 <b>Neptune RAT Variant Spreads via YouTube, Telegram</b><br>
    Disguised as legit tools, installs ransomware + keyloggers. Evades via emojis and Arabic text.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://hackread.com/neptune-rat-variant-youtube-steal-windows-passwords/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

